OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy across the north of the
OL,6,Fcountry with patchy rain in northwest
OL,7,FScotland. A few isolated showers are
OL,8,Falso possible across the far east of
OL,9,FEngland. Fine elsewhere, with hazy
OL,10,Fsunshine and feeling very warm,
OL,11,Fparticularly in the south
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FPatchy light rain sinking
OL,14,Fsoutheast across parts of Scotland and
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland overnight. Otherwise
OL,16,Fdry, with variable amounts of cloud.
OL,17,FWarm for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
