OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy across the north and
OL,6,Fwest with outbreaks of light rain or
OL,7,Fshowers, especially during the
OL,8,Fafternoon and evening. Dry elsewhere
OL,9,Fwith very warm sunshine, locally hot
OL,10,Fin the south.
